page_0: "Honored Alarius,

I have always valued your expertise as a jeweller, and I am currently in the position of making an offer that undoubtedly will be most appealing to you. As I would like to discuss matters in person, I hereby invite you to visit our summer estate for dinner. Just send a reply naming the day that is to your convenience, and I shall provide you with a carriage.

Sincerely,
Lord Edward Farrington"
